寧願返地盤"},{"pid":"53161a4039a2bab06901b9d91716ed2e7d75baa8","tid":519323,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86018ab9578e15c0fb8f672c1be14c4ec06e211","tid":519323,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家要落場既無人做啦下麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲食業嘅仲大撚把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我就係講飲食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家開始好多都唔洗落啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀。仲好普遍，所以好少後生仔入行，佢地寧願返地盤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"因為我有FD都係做飲食, 佢地話而家有落場既狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前讀書都有番過下P.T, 好彩既就係識到D朋友一齊落場去篤波, 唔係三四個鍾都唔知係度做乜撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1653acfcfb32a750fed858c13e4bcbf4e649c40","tid":519323,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家要落場既無人做啦下麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲食業嘅仲大撚把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我就係講飲食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家開始好多都唔洗落啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀。仲好普遍，所以好少後生仔入行，佢地寧願返地盤</blockquote>因為我有FD都係做飲食, 佢地話而家有落場既狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前讀書都有番過下P.T, 好彩既就係識到D朋友一齊落場去篤波, 唔係三四個鍾都唔知係度做乜撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪無後生做囉，而且係華人先頂到咁奴性嘅安排"}]}